      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 240ºC/ 220ºC (fan)/ gas 9</p><p>Crush your <strong>garlic</strong> open by squashing them with the side of a knife and discard the skins</p><p>Cut your <strong>red chilli[es]</strong> in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and chop roughly</p><p>Tip: Like it hot? Keep the seeds in!</p>",
