            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>Tenderstem broccoli </strong>and<strong> spinach</strong> to a large piece of <strong>tin foil</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> and a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Scrunch the foil around the vegetables to form a tightly sealed parcel and add to a baking tray</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 10-12 min or until the Tenderstem broccoli is tender with a slight bite – these are your <strong>greens</strong></p>",
