    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [4 tbsp]</span> <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>chilli paste</strong> to the pan and cook for 2-3 min, stirring frequently until fragrant</p><p>Boil half a kettle</p>",
      "order": 6,
