            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Thai-style pad cha basa</strong> over the <strong>fragrant</strong> <strong>rice </strong>with the<strong> greens </strong>to the side</p><p>Pour any <strong>remaining sauce</strong> from the pan over the basa</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>coriander leaves</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
